    "On the other hand, deep learning models were used, which are CNN, Recurrent Neural Network (RNN) and, Convolutional RNN (CRNN).",
    "Both experiments with machine learning and deep learning used different representation features, including word frequency and word embedding.",
    "The XGB showed the highest accuracy in detecting misinformation in this study.",
    "Study in [73] collected datasets about the COVID-19 pandemic from Twitter on the types of fake news and misinformation to detect fake news.",
    "The tweets were annotated in two ways: manual and automatic."
